50 Coins weight 1 lb

Copper   =    1 Copper = 1/10 Silver = 1/50 Electrum = 1/100 Gold = 1/1000 Platinum
Silver   =   10 Copper =    1 Silver =  1/5 Electrum =  1/10 Gold =  1/100 Platinum
Electrum =   50 Copper =    5 Silver =    1 Electrum =   1/2 Gold =   1/20 Platinum
Gold     =  100 Copper =   10 Silver =    2 Electrum =     1 Gold =   1/10 Platinum
Platinum = 1000 Copper =  100 Silver =   20 Electrum =    10 Gold =      1 Platinum
